original_title: NPP and ‘Sarvajana Balaya’ National List MPs gazetted
original_body_lines: The names nominated to enter the Parliament through the National Lists of the National People’s Power (NPP) and the ‘Sarvajana Balaya’ alliance, have been gazetted.
